2026-05-13T20:16:27.9652535Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-13T20:16:27.9653124Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-13T20:16:27.9653717Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-13T20:16:27.9654306Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-13T20:16:27.9654846Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-13T20:16:27.9655425Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
